title: Radiant Touch
description:
These ensemble compositions for grand piano, violin, guitar, and gentle atmospheric percussion all utilize Oliver's principle of "harmonic resonance" to move you to truly feel this music and the inner peace that it instills.

Here he is joined by his World Ensemble of flutes, guitar, sitar, mbira, sax, fretless bass, zither, didgeridoo, and Tibetan bowls to create soothing, universal music that crosses all borders and musical styles.
